indimail-mta (2.4-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * svctool - added option to refresh services
  * moved cdbget, cdbgetm,cdbmake, qmail-getpw, qmail-local, qmail-newmrh to sbin
  * moved system binaries to sbin
  * added permissions files for openSUSE
  * svctool - use SHA-512 encryption for indisrvr admin password
  * svctool - moved enabling/disabling of services to separate functions --enable-service, --disable-service
  * create ld.so cache only when libdir is not /usr/lib or /usr/lib64
  * svctool - added --ssl, --require-secure-transport command line option for mysqld
  * svctool - create env variable VIRTUAL_PKG_LIB with libindimail.so to provide indimail functionality
  * BUG - indimail_stub.c:  fixed spurious chown() in r_mkdir()
  * svctool - fix creation of env variable VIRTUAL_PKG_LIB

 -- Manvendra Bhangui <manvendra@indimail.org>  Sat, 31 Mar 2018 00:01:12 +0530
